{
  "annotations": [
    {
      "start_time": 0,
      "end_time": 356,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "text": "“Esa, esa Dominé” Don Rafael Cepeda Atiles",
          "bold": true
        },
        {
          "type": "line-break",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "children"
        },
        {
          "type": "line-break",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "That one, that one, Dominé\nThat one, that one, Dominé\nThat one, that one, Dominé\nMy savior of living strength"
        },
        {
          "type": "line-break",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "children"
        },
        {
          "type": "line-break",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Tell Valentín\nWhat Manuel told him:\nNot to go to the bomba if Paulé wasn’t dancing"
        },
        {
          "type": "line-break",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Ay, yesterday I saw Urubina\nShe told me, “What do you want?”\nIf you light a candle for her, you must light it upside down"
        },
        {
          "type": "line-break",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "They’re already buzzing together\nAlong the Portugués River\nShe carries a spell in her hand\nTo win over José"
        },
        {
          "type": "line-break",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "That one, that one, Dominé\nThat one, that one, Shangoté\nThat one, that one, living strength\nMy savior of Shangoté"
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "bomba",
          "category": "genre"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "3710ee3b-4aca-4efd-80c2-3f20c7d10ee4"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 357,
      "end_time": 462,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "text": "“Son más divina” Don Rafael Cepeda Atiles",
          "bold": true
        },
        {
          "type": "line-break",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "children"
        },
        {
          "type": "line-break",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "They are, they are more divine"
        },
        {
          "type": "line-break",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "children"
        },
        {
          "type": "line-break",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "More divine, they sway in balance\nMore divine, they are (I am Laré)\nMore divine, they sway in balance"
        }
      ],
