    {
      "start_time": 995,
      "end_time": 1020,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "The music of Cangrejos en el río is one of those traditions well known on the farms, where they light up the riverbeds to find the roe and prepare the sacks to gather the catch. Beautifully performed by the Cepeda family. Let us continue with La Borucana. "
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
